channel.title: ~~xyst~~ 317 team of one or two members wanted!
channel.description:
Hey guys! First let me start of by saying Whoo Hooo it's summer! I'm an okay coder (can't do much client sided) and I am looking for team with one or two people to make a really good server. If we do get this up we will split the profits (after excepting donations and such) I can almost guarantee you guys that we can actually make this happen.
Server Name: [b]~~xyst~~[/b] VPS: [b]coming soon!~[/b] (will cost around 15-30$) Website: [b]coming soon!~[/b] (will cost around 3-10$ domain / unknown for webhost)
I have wanted a good server for quite a while and after failing very bad many times I have turned for help from my fellow moparscapians.
P.S. I have some code that i wrote myself including ancients, farming, summoning and commands. Stuff like that is the easy part. Hope to see you on the ~~xyst~~ team! :)
_____
Media: [b]coming soon!~[/b]
